Required Components:
  1. Access & view individual player stats, team stats
  2. Allow users to make a hypothetical trade based on salary matching
  3. List out all possible players a single player/package of players can be traded for
  4. View team finances in a visual manner

Future:
  1. Trade Finder: Create CPU trades based on player stats, team needs, historical precedence
  2. Create best fits for players based on money/team needs/player wants for trades
  3. Create best free agent destinations for every players based on team needs/player perceived salary/stats
  4. View the finances, players, transactions for every single team -> ie we can see the Lakers from 2010 to Present
